{"tid":1031723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"🔥【培正小學】🔥訓導主任 煽動校園欺凌","createTime":"2019-02-22T00:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T03:33:17.000Z","uid":176272,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5485148d7fc1c80ed9f526a699194235b81329a4","tid":1031723,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:08:00.000Z","msg":"事情經過<br />\n語言欺凌:&nbsp;2017新學年，受害人(下稱X) 收到班上男仔(下稱李)匿名寫比佢嘅字條，內容包括恐嚇X，預言X嘅父母會死。類似字條一共有5張，已經令到X日日好唔安落。 X比咗字條班主任(劉)睇，但劉話只係一般紙仔完全唔處理，仲沒收咗部份字條。&nbsp;<br />\n身體欺凌:&nbsp;11月李開始打X背部。X同劉講，劉依然話唔想處理，話件事交比訓導(下稱黃)算。&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個星期後李小息時又打X，X不適到當晚就要父母帶佢睇醫生(所以有醫生紙證明呢件事)。父母同黃講，黃稱上星期嘅打人事件因為已經一個星期，所以file closed&nbsp;，話會調查吓今次。<br />\n打人嘅時候X有朋友見到，後尾訓導洗腦個朋友話無呢件事發生過，黃之後便聲稱調查後搵唔到目擊證人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nX 父母一路有搵證據比黃，但黃話全部唔成立。後尾黃聲稱打人事件證據不足，所以又可以close file&nbsp;(真係龍門任佢擺)<br />\nX父母搵培正社工講，社工淨係話自己就黎退休，唔想搞咁多野就無處理到。&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩件打人事件close file之後，黃就帶頭欺凌X。&nbsp;<br />\n1.黃去X班房叫大家遠離X，X一時之間無哂朋友，精神嚴重崩潰&nbsp;<br />\n2.黃係小息時段, 搵兩個低年級同學跟著X去廁所,X形容好似係黑社會一樣, 非常恐怖. 身心受到極大傷害(X亦因此嚇到唔敢去廁所)&nbsp;<br />\n3.黃屈X寫影響校風紙條並傳開去, (X表示沒有寫這紙仔, 更不是他的字跡, 要討回公道)&nbsp;<br />\n4.黃恐嚇X如果再講大話訧要叫註校警宫王警長處分X<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真心想知，點解成間學校無一個人做到野? 本身打人事件老師好好處理就無野，但老師個個推卸責任，仲帶頭玩9學生<br />\n培正小學真心cls希望大家幫幫手推post，等所有人見到呢間小學有幾醜惡</span>"},{"pid":"a1d9fc0ce297e37ddf572387f0c1509ab1d08d2f","tid":1031723,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:09:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190222/59287780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190222%2F59287780&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=b2dd037f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190222%2F59287780&h=87371cb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190222/59287780</a>"},{"pid":"5f15ea71322f051ef84e1ccd181fa69ae1a02f33","tid":1031723,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:11:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/298046/%E5%9F%B9%E6%AD%A3%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%96%91%E7%88%86%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-%E5%B0%8F%E5%9B%9B%E7%94%9F%E7%A8%B1%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E6%89%93%E5%85%BC%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%AA%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F298046%2F%25E5%259F%25B9%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%25AC%25BA%25E5%2587%258C%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2585%25BC%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%259A%2587-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=88e85f1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/298046/%E5%9F%B9%E6%AD%A3%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%96%91%E7%88%86%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-%E5%B0%8F%E5%9B%9B%E7%94%9F%E7%A8%B1%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E6%89%93%E5%85%BC%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%AA%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89</a>"},{"pid":"cf42b497cfb32ab92869d61a3c5957b9024f07b3","tid":1031723,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:14:51.000Z","msg":"原post:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求救，有小學老師煽動校園欺凌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1030008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1030008</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"}