\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2276759%2F%25E5%259F%25B9%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2587%25B7%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25AC%25BA%25E5%2587%258C%25E9%2586%259C%25E8%2581%259E%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25AC%25BA%25E5%2587%258C%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E6%25BD%25B0&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=27943724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2276759/%E5%9F%B9%E6%AD%A3%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%88%86%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C%E9%86%9C%E8%81%9E%E3%80%80%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%B8%B6%E9%A0%AD%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C%E5%B0%8F%E5%9B%9B%E7%94%9F%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0</a>"},{"pid":"0f2c936bcdc9d8243bf7e837a42d04e099276261","tid":1031723,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:21:01.000Z","msg":"傳統名校培正小學疑爆校園欺凌醜聞！日前有網民深夜在連登討論區爆料指，該校小四男生遭同班同學多次「傳紙仔」恐嚇，更遭對方兩度襲擊。受害男生家長表示曾舉報事件，惟多名老師、駐校社工以至校長均拒絕受理。最終受害人承受巨大壓力而轉校，至今仍留下心理陰影。受害人與家長現身向傳媒指控校方是非黑白不分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190222/59287780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190222%2F59287780&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=b2dd037f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190222%2F59287780&h=87371cb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190222/59287780</a>"},{"pid":"298061b786cd1deda79b7b41498eb3f704128ba2","tid":1031723,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024832571b5303c7daaaba9b6034d4f2e3fa42fe","tid":1031723,"uid":107447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:23:49.000Z","msg":"多行不義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b100b055d8b88fb4b5ab1e506eea4dabc3baa3b8","tid":1031723,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"培正小學爆出懷疑校園欺凌事件，一名小四男生聲稱被同學打背部，兼收到匿名字條恐嚇，預言父母會死。男生家長指先後向班主任及訓導主任求助，但以證據不足了事。<br />\n男生家長亦指訓導主任叫同學遠離男生，又於小息時段派兩名同學跟着該名男生上廁所，令其精神飽受困擾。受到欺凌後，男生曾出現輕生念頭，幸得朋友勸喻才避免悲劇發生，最後男生於去年1月轉校。家長表示，公開事件是希望得到校方及涉事的老師向他們一家道歉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/298046/%E5%9F%B9%E6%AD%A3%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%96%91%E7%88%86%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-%E5%B0%8F%E5%9B%9B%E7%94%9F%E7%A8%B1%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E6%89%93%E5%85%BC%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%AA%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F298046%2F%25E5%259F%25B9%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%25AC%25BA%25E5%2587%258C%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2585%25BC%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%259A%2587-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=88e85f1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/298046/%E5%9F%B9%E6%AD%A3%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E7%96%91%E7%88%86%E6%AC%BA%E5%87%8C%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-%E5%B0%8F%E5%9B%9B%E7%94%9F%E7%A8%B1%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E6%89%93%E5%85%BC%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%AA%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89</a>"},{"pid":"fdbc113a0c728bcf609c2201f0c7751df0574565","ti